    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自选技能，装备合成，搭配出各种意想不到的组合然后享受割草的快乐吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从这里开始你愉快的冒险吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241720/extras/dad9426e086c9922303a563b2d28360f.poster.avif?t=1729828763\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241720/extras/dad9426e086c9922303a563b2d28360f.webm?t=1729828763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241720/extras/dad9426e086c9922303a563b2d28360f.mp4?t=1729828763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >首先选择你的角色开始冒险，每波冒险开始的时候购买物品，商店内的物品还可以合成为高级物品。在冒险的过程中角色会提升等级，随着等级的提升角色会最终选取4个技能来提升战斗能力。怪物会随着波次数量越来越强，在这个过程中你需要有选择性的提升自己的能力来完成全部冒险历程。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自动战斗，你只需要负责灵活走位就可以了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自选技能，在80多项技能中选择4项搭配来构成你的角色技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装备合成，百余种装备提供给你丰富的构筑路线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色多样，有20多个角色任你挑选。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态难度，每波开始之前你都可以选择一次难度选项。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多样化武器</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内有各种类型的武器，带来不同的冒险体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241720/extras/16b03fa628c9d4a9c1eabf496b8d91ca.poster.avif?t=1729828763\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241720/extras/16b03fa628c9d4a9c1eabf496b8d91ca.webm?t=1729828763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241720/extras/16b03fa628c9d4a9c1eabf496b8d91ca.mp4?t=1729828763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>装备合成</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >低阶装备合成为高级装备，有计划的构筑成型。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241720/extras/31e85f4969650a77677fb4d13526d4b3.poster.avif?t=1729828763\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241720/extras/31e85f4969650a77677fb4d13526d4b3.webm?t=1729828763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241720/extras/31e85f4969650a77677fb4d13526d4b3.mp4?t=1729828763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>任选技能</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在全部的技能池中任意挑选，后期还可以重选技能，根据局势灵活变换。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241720/extras/c41cef3a4e2a4fc065a4524cf7953e61.poster.avif?t=1729828763\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241720/extras/c41cef3a4e2a4fc065a4524cf7953e61.webm?t=1729828763\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241720/extras/c41cef3a4e2a4fc065a4524cf7953e61.mp4?t=1729828763\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>快速更新</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎加入qq群954023988提出您的宝贵建议或者创意脑洞，好的创意会迅速加入到游戏更新。</p>",
